ct categories.	2021-04-28 06:24:45.5748+00	2021-10-04 15:28:45.485966+00	\N	\N	APPROVED	https://www.draper.com/	https://storage.googleapis.com/akvo-unep-gpml/images/technology_003.jpg	https://storage.googleapis.com/akvo-unep-gpml/images/technology_03_logo.jpeg	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	f	\N	f	en	f	gpml
